content:
Tradewind's blockchain-based platform called VaultChain (built by R3 using its Corda network), allows users to buy and sell gold and silver more efficiently. Some "top institutions and wholesalers" are Tradewind's clients, who themselves have "high net worth" clientele, including producers, industrial users, wholesalers and jewelers, the firm told The Block.<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
<br data-v-f87c67ca="">
"Buyers and sellers of precious metals on our platform purchase these hard assets via a network of dealers who use our product. The asset they buy is an asset held at the Royal Canadian Mint—with title clearly reflected on the ledger," it added.&nbsp;
